    <item>
      <title>智利总统鲍里（Borcor）承受大规模停电的影响</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-03/boric-weathers-storm-after-massive-blackout-as-chile-vote-nears</link>
      <description><![CDATA[智利十年来，智利最大的停电毫不动摇，加布里埃尔·博里奇（Gabriel Boric）总统的受欢迎程度毫不费力，因为该国努力发现那些负责罕见的失败的人，使大多数人口陷入黑暗，并停止了世界上最大的铜矿。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-03/boric-weathers-storm-after-massive-blackout-as-chile-vote-nears</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Mar 2025 14:07:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>核监督机构说，特朗普在伊朗的下一步范围内迫在眉睫</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-03/nuclear-watchdog-says-trump-looms-large-over-next-steps-in-iran</link>
      <description><![CDATA[联合国核监管机构呼吁美国和伊朗开始谈判，这表明美国总统唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）采取了下一步行动，试图在其原子活动上与伊斯兰共和国的紧张局势进行抗辩。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-03/nuclear-watchdog-says-trump-looms-large-over-next-steps-in-iran</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Mar 2025 13:36:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普袭击乌克兰的Zelenskiy时，有什么危险</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-03/after-trump-zelenskiy-talks-collapse-what-s-at-stake</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国总统唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）长期表示，他将迅速结束俄罗斯在乌克兰的战争。为了达成协议，美国已经与克里姆林宫官员进行了直接讨论，乌克兰和欧洲大国在谈判中占据一席之地。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-03/after-trump-zelenskiy-talks-collapse-what-s-at-stake</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Mar 2025 12:32:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>梅尔斯希望本周在德国国防上与SPD打交道</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-03/germany-explores-options-for-defense-and-infrastructure-spending</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德国总理弗里德里希·梅尔斯（Friedrich Merz）说，他希望与社会民主党人达成协议，以提高国防支出，以在欧盟领导人周四在布鲁塞尔开会之前。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-03/germany-explores-options-for-defense-and-infrastructure-spending</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Mar 2025 09:40:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普的仇恨推动投资者重新申请乌克兰和平交易</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-03/ukraine-bonds-drop-as-trump-feud-shakes-up-east-european-trades</link>
      <description><![CDATA[自去年重组以来，乌克兰的债券在投资者对近期和平前景的期望之后的期望之后，这是自去年重组以来的最多滑行。]]></description>
